<p class="indent4" style="-uslm-lc:I16" xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">In the case of a taxpayer who enters into a written binding contract before <date date="2017-12-15">December 15, 2017</date>, to close on the purchase of a principal residence before <date date="2018-01-01">January 1, 2018</date>, and who purchases such residence before <date date="2018-04-01">April 1, 2018</date>, subclause (III) shall be applied by substituting “<date date="2018-04-01">April 1, 2018</date>” for “<date date="2017-12-15">December 15, 2017</date>”.</p>
